<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="448" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1539,1744]" pageId="3" pageNumber="448">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1683,1708]" pageId="3" pageNumber="448">Etymology.</emphasis>
The new species is named in honour of the late Dr. Jean Clastrier (
<date box="[1103,1232,1684,1708]" pageId="3" pageNumber="448" value="1910" valueMax="1997">
<number box="[1103,1232,1684,1708]" pageId="3" pageNumber="448" value="1953.5" valueMax="1997.0" valueMin="1910.0">1910–1997</number>
</date>
